data.text:
Praise the Lord! Thank You God for Your Forgiveness and Your Grace! I accidentally posted something that could have been taken wrong and I’m so sorry. It showed a laughing response instead of the intended caring response. I pray anyone who saw it will forgive me for not being more careful when posting things online. Please pray for my health needs, financial needs, my family and loved ones, my friends and acquaintances, my caretakers and those important to them, and my dog and my truck. Please pray and ask God to gently draw us into a tighter relationship with Him. May His Will be Done in all of our Lives. May He protect us from the lies and the deceitful nature of the enemy. Please pray that we will all spend more time praying in Jesus Name, and Praising God for all He Does and is Doing in our Lives and the Lives of those who we pray for. Praise the Lord!
